 "title": "Orson's Departure",
 "summary": "Aboard a ship streaking through hyperspace, the mechanic Orson and the Jedi Jessalyn Valios share a bittersweet parting as their paths diverge. The two, grown close through Orson's Force training and shared trials, reflect on what they have meant to one another before he goes his own way. Their quiet exchange is tinged with affection and the ache of separation. The departure closes a chapter in the unlikely bond between the gruff technician and his Jedi companion.",
